story.text: New York definitely suits me to a certain extent. The will of the people here is extraordinary - people have opportunities and they seize them. If it were not for her inherent vulnerability, I would move here. But, I think I will join a club in the city and stay here more often.
Perhaps Kamilla will get a place here. Or perhaps I will split a place with someone else.
I want to export a bit of New York and a bit of San Francisco to New Switzerland.
The biggest burden of the city is the food. Finding a solution to the food and water problem without electricity is key.
The tiny city must be able to function with computer and without computers. Swappable Manual for Automatic transmission. This will be one of the more important innovations.
